{"tid":388423,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"日本女高中生英勇救貓 - 如果見到有隻貓仔喺馬路上你會點做？","createTime":"2017-09-05T12:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T02:59:37.000Z","uid":34252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2693807c091424d5edbe1832dfe4d7cc88ae553d","tid":388423,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdA5QJi4T6I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqdA5QJi4T6I&d=gJGV%2FGGIthcadGnvJRRIY6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=18bdd9a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdA5QJi4T6I</a><br />\n<br />\n如果見到有隻貓仔喺馬路上你會點做？京都堀川通七条就有隻黑貓衝咗出馬路仲畀撞埋車度，後面留意到嘅司機即時停車，亦有電單車司機將架車駛埋一邊準備落車救佢，不過最快手都係路過嘅女高中生，二話不說就丟低書包衝出去抱走貓貓！"},{"pid":"a1ed27b3678c7bdba0aa3387006852151c2d0d8f","tid":388423,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"快點拯救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e789f356d37260897a990e1971d40970b1aa572c","tid":388423,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"貓可能已被左後轆車到"},{"pid":"d997a2af098799aa2c23081d23c04c65298a34e2","tid":388423,"uid":34252,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"幾大就幾大。為左救貓貓一命，唔好講金，我命都可以唔要。"},{"pid":"c2f0ee3592b26abee1ba5eb38bc0ae9060724f87","tid":388423,"uid":35370,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"貓之報恩個開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5ebce4e5a4d90230510b924000723c76713fac","tid":388423,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"香港成日見到啲貓俾車轆到成塊地毯咁。"},{"pid":"b1bd604f7dbcf1e4a27e6bd53b2323c51d66d336","tid":388423,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港成日見